Number two.
you couldn't meet with women.

255
00:12:34.125 --> 00:12:36.207
Number three. you couldn't
take pictures of anything.

256
00:12:36.290 --> 00:12:38.542
I had a camera. a small camera.

257
00:12:38.625 --> 00:12:40.709
